revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== From {{der|en|yij|yandy}}. ===Pronunciation=== * {{audio|en|en-au-yandy.ogg|Audio (AU)}} ===Verb=== {{en-verb}} # {{lb|en|Australia}} To [[separate]] (grain or pieces of mineral) by shaking in a special shallow [[dish]] ===Noun=== {{en-noun}} # {{lb|en|Australia}} The dish used in this process
